    'wr_content' => '<p><span style="color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">[대한경제=박흥순 기자] 지난달 건설현장 10곳 중 1곳은 콘크리트 보온 양생을 위해 갈탄·숯탄을 사용한 것으로 나타났다. 갈탄·숯탄은 질식사고를 유발할 수 있어 고용당국에서 사용을 자제하고 있으나, 가격이 저렴하고 보관이 편리하다는 이유로 여전히 일부 건설현장에서 활용되고 있다.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;" align="center"><span style="color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://www.cjchem.co.kr/data/editor/2410/524f162af497b551dcc7f927d955fbb4_1728868494_92.jpg" title="524f162af497b551dcc7f927d955fbb4_1728868494_92.jpg" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;"><br style="clear:both;"></span><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">건설현장의 콘크리트 보온 양생을 위해 피워놓은 갈탄. /사진:경기도소방재난본부 제공</span><span style="color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;" align="center"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-da7d4cff-c48b-480c-816a-fe8ea14d0666" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset " id="SE-ed655c54-11e4-458b-b3aa-758465dc9589" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">18일 건설업계와 건설노조에 따르면, 전국 건설현장의 9.8%에서 동절기 콘크리트 보온 양생에 갈탄·숯탄을 사용 중인 것으로 조사됐다. 갈탄·숯탄은 상대적으로 기온이 더 낮은 중부지방 건설현장에서 더 많이 쓰였다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-a5e59d44-1ebb-499f-aea3-5a10b6c0f87b" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-f1892324-6f2a-4558-982c-ff49c1562134" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(109, 109, 109);">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-27a7312c-fa72-47b5-831e-301f2a9c76f3" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset " id="SE-d06320fb-51ca-4179-a65d-0154ec902482" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">날씨가 추운 겨울에는 콘크리트가 잘 마르지 않아 타설 작업 후 현장을 밀폐하고 난로를 켜는 방식으로 양생작업을 진행한다. 이때 갈탄·숯탄·야자탄 등을 사용하면 일산화탄소가 대량 발생해 질식사고로 이어질 수 있다. 최근 10년 간 겨울철 건설현장에서 발생한 질식사고는 총 27건으로 이 중 67%에 달하는 18건이 콘크리트 보온양생 중 발생했다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-eb05c119-c547-4aee-9ae0-dedb954e5cb6" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-6345550e-2d3e-414f-b6a7-9ff73839205d" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(109, 109, 109);">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-9eb66303-bc14-4ff1-8477-58645f347796" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset " id="SE-ef6f3fb9-daa4-4431-8832-a36086b30061" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">그나마 최근에는 정부·노조의 적극적인 움직임으로 갈탄의 사용이 크게 줄었다. 콘크리트 보온 양생에 등유 열풍기를 사용하는 건설현장은 48.8%, 전기 열풍기는 14.6%로 나타났다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-60bb8d2a-1a7f-4db6-a516-0eb4e6b4c9a5" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-db9c49cd-7712-4d52-abc2-5f3b42d5e828" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(109, 109, 109);">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-55ad7796-778f-4d19-a684-93cf6073226f" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset " id="SE-0e2b5555-79cd-4af8-bf26-e45b582f5e7b" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">대형건설사들은 질식사고 예방을 위해 갈탄 사용을 자제하고 있다. 포스코이앤씨는 갈탄·숯탄의 반입을 금지하고 에탄올만 연료로 사용하고 있다. 롯데건설은 질식사고 예방을 위해 심폐소생술 교육을 진행하며, GS건설은 콘크리트 보온 양생작업 시 질식사고 예방을 위해 양생구간 출입 전 가스농도를 미리 측정하고 있다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-f028d3e3-6412-429d-9846-d4299cd8c2fb" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-85ecaa6b-58e0-48a7-8af7-54ade943a71c" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(109, 109, 109);">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-05a7efa7-3726-4f0f-8675-0da8db7886a1" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset " id="SE-7d0cf1ca-eeb3-45ab-9132-4863b0ed0bca" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">문제는 중소건설사다. 중소건설사는 많은 인력과 예산을 투입할 수 있는 대형건설사에 비해 여건이 녹록치 않아 값이 저렴한 갈탄을 사용하면서도 각종 안전수칙을 소홀히 하는 경향이 있다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-b75e8c90-e7b0-4cbc-801b-881e3e96cfeb" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-6e6a559e-c218-4227-a5df-fa78c10c263b" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(109, 109, 109);">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-0ffeddc7-0aed-4c83-a9c1-fca02e47d59a" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset " id="SE-ae875d12-9a43-427e-a2b5-de242858cf7f" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">한 중소건설사 안전관리자는 “지하슬라브는 일산화탄소 질식 위험이 커 열풍기를 사용하지만 세대 기준층에서는 통상 갈탄·숯탄을 사용한다”며 “갈탄 사용 금지가 아니고 지양이기 때문”이라고 말했다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-0a5e0d50-671c-48c1-885a-08770bf8a6ea" style="box-sizing: unset; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, arial, 나눔고딕, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: break-spaces; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs16 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-09bd4e62-8549-4aff-8822-5a438be504a4" style="box-sizing: unset; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: se-nanumgothi