    'wr_content' => '<p>&nbsp;</p><div align="center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.cjchem.co.kr/data/editor/2208/c3b892f8b32962c2777d5c33ca8fea04_1661840227_89.jpg" title="c3b892f8b32962c2777d5c33ca8fea04_1661840227_89.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-dd154000-5aa2-4cf4-b33c-d812f7dcebdb" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-6cbb4424-13eb-4e4f-8aab-d6d33a49a979" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">직업병을 일으키는 원인은 크게 △소음·진동 등 물리적 인자 △</span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-d37859a9-1d5a-447d-a007-6db3bf5d8cbc" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">중금속·유기용제 등 독성을 가진 화학적 인자</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-53cdf919-7620-4b08-a8bd-6ab91336f7d9" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"> △병원균·공기오염 등 생물학적 인자 △스트레스 등의 사회·심리적 요소로 나눠볼 수 있습니다. 우선 화학적 인자에 따른 직업병에 대해 설명해보려 합니다. 제조·건설업 등 현장직에 종사하는 근로자들은 원료이든 가공과정에서 발생한 부산물이든 늘 화학인자에 노출될 수밖에 없는데요.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-6b9c391a-5eaa-4f5a-b77d-caddc53e1c9b" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-b00b159c-caed-492c-b96b-6ed7f414f6a0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-b5505ba7-13cb-4351-8ffc-4a84697612ce" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-9f4897c5-9acf-4676-bebc-b938c181f8c0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">이에 따른 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-a25d8e8d-252a-4023-bd52-f2516259a428" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">급성·만성 중독</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-1d05850a-7f34-49e9-96fe-b8a8569ed4c9" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">으로 여러 직업병에 이환되는 경우가 적지 않습니다. 우리나라에 산업재해보상보험이 도입된 것은 1964년입니다. 당시에는 상시근로자수가 500인 이상인 제조업과 광업에만 적용됐습니다. 산재법 제정 전인 1959년부터 대한석탄공사에서 진폐증에 대해서는 보상제도를 마련했습니다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-ce45ba54-8249-4e62-b55d-6f1dd6d90c20" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-324dfada-d448-451a-b1ef-d2d5949d35c4" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-f33be6f0-8541-4258-97d6-6189400c552c" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-8dd2beb2-2326-44c4-b9b5-4a0f0e699f00" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">이 무렵에는</span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-9f7eb757-d436-446c-8121-08c48d0af292" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"> 진폐증</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-32642b2f-9796-45b8-af44-0b86c61c370d" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">을 제외한 직업병에 대해 산재임을 쉽게 인정해 주지 않았는데요. 1966년부터 가동돼 1993년 폐업한 A사 인견공장에서 다수 근로자가 동시에 콩팥손상, 사지마비, 언어장애 등의 증상을 겪게 됐습니다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-c7cf4fae-25fa-4634-82fb-6349aef86baf" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-d092a5d6-3036-4317-9121-5b176c71544e" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-84de7f3d-5283-4323-a993-47027862284d" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-5a61b880-abdd-4a81-9f0b-e4c7fc64bfcd" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">근로자들이 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-efddb906-1da7-434e-94ec-45764114a3a9" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">이황화탄소(CS₂)</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-2090b0b7-a6d5-4665-8c28-d077c579bc08" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"> 중독</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-28c14f40-1306-4355-ab17-1bb0fd988d25" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">임을 인지하고 산재신청을 요구하자 사업주가 산재임을 부정하했는데요. A사 근로자와 그 가족들이 집단적으로 투쟁한 결과 1988년 근로자 21명에 대해 직업병임을 인정받게 됩니다. 이는 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-4518dc93-585a-4cf6-a81b-42435182a239" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">진폐증</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-a0d2b339-d8a8-4765-bd36-069d044ec9bb" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">과 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-045ec324-0cde-4bd8-aa23-20d5283d4ae8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">소음성 난청</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-3e7d1f89-5859-41c2-9359-6ad2edd676d1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">에 이어 세 번째로 인정된 직업병입니다. 이후 계속된 투쟁으로 현재 1000명에 가까운 피해자가 산재보험의 혜택을 받게 됐는데요. 이는 현재까지 국내 최대 규모의 독성물질에 의한 직업병 발병 사례로 꼽히며 2010년부터는 이황화탄소중독증을 진단받은 경우 업무상질병판정위원회의 심의를 생략하고 산업재해임을 비교적 빠르게 인정받을 수 있습니다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-0adab51f-3253-448f-ad68-92c4135157ff" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-0ecfdc34-e92f-441d-ac6c-6d9ba69b1ead" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-91b44d2c-21a8-4834-afde-2841ac652562" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset " id="SE-14a110b7-411e-4b4d-b081-1571b79d23e9" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">1988년에는 온도계 공장에서 일하던 고등학생이 </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-f755e04c-350e-4ef9-9d51-1c4b067b59fd" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">수은 중독</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset " id="SE-f274e61c-4b25-4b35-a4a6-988b5738b34b" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">으로 사망하는 사건</u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-f1eb442c-7a88-4c54-898b-a2fbb24bddf3" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">이 있었습니다. 1990년대에는 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-ab0eef52-0189-4c8a-99d6-82775ad06e5f" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">건전지 재생공장에서 카드뮴에 노출된 근로자가 </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-4fb4de46-5916-4f05-ad88-f4fe31d2d2d5" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">신장질환</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-40f36a96-8ff8-4ebb-bcdb-18269f7a0fde" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">에 이환된 사례</u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-2ae1666a-4e79-4e96-a27d-db181c9678e6" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">가 있었는데요. 2000년대에는</span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-76cfd91a-59f1-43e9-9eee-c1bbe28a9fe4" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"> 반도체공장에서 일하던 근로자가 </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-87ea75a1-f69e-495a-b072-69e5c3d747e2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">트리클로로에틸렌, 시너</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-fbe43435-8d57-46aa-9b5c-349ff930f05c" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"> 등의 발암물질에 만성적으로 노출돼 </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-9a8dc175-5492-4ada-a3dc-ceb4b064c2da" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">백혈병</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-127ed979-47ea-495f-af07-44128ace937c" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">을 비롯한</u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-6b4277c3-db92-40ca-a665-1dcbe551ae91" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"> 희귀암</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-7ce817cf-420e-4859-852c-e240be935bea" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">에 걸리는 일</u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-f02aa6d7-1159-472b-a2cf-f60348b05c1f" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">이 있었습니다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-bc93d1a9-2d77-4e48-bc2d-fbc4e84f0008" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-6c68dffe-6c27-4b11-a1df-8f72b02b7e49" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-8f47dfa9-59f8-4ac0-af9f-4f92e8fb9104" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-8216ff09-6bd7-4655-b617-de1d1c9dd09d" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">2016년에는 휴대전화 스크린 제조 공장에서 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-c0413843-72da-4387-9d99-2ea42e3ae141" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">냉각제로 </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-f31e31ab-7232-4093-9695-0d85ea6de127" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">메탄올</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-8a4ab607-a1f7-4ff6-8739-687675596fc0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">을 사용해 근로자 다수가 </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-fe875130-4340-403c-8c4c-42d7418ec6bf" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">시신경 또는 중추신경에 손상</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-b6bbc75f-0064-472b-a912-3e71901440eb" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">을 입어 실명하거나 </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-8424b9cc-a7e9-4a0a-848a-a3a10c712bdf" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">뇌병변 장애</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-eb0fd45b-ec41-41ec-a5ce-fa5ec2c366ba" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">를 얻게 됐습니다. 2022년 3월에는 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-430bfdcf-fa60-4082-80b3-309357daba7a" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">트리클로로메탄</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-5bf5206c-20c9-4953-9ddb-55a02be288e1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">에 급성으로 중독된 근로자 16인이 </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-d407b870-ab1c-42fb-aebe-b35ab844bace" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">간 손상</span></u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-8db53a72-4817-4eee-87bc-44cd88223c83" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">을 입는 일</u></