라고 불리기도 합니다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-ef87a1d8-362e-4ff2-b1c5-d54e05269f7f" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-b843fc67-1767-4b74-8220-fdfca5a36e9e" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-27d881c2-b216-452b-b58f-f4b7a3e7a3e5" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-4d9787f7-5aff-41b6-9c9f-207bdce667d2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">비소를 소화기관으로 섭취하게 되면 마비·경련·혼수 등으로 사망할 수도 있습니다. 또 회복하더라도 말초신경염과 골수기능 저하 등이 나타날 수 있는데요. 입을 통한 섭취로 일어나는 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-  se-style-unset " id="SE-a6555c53-3f37-4b00-8f66-32a4d9f08170" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align