    'wr_content' => '<blockquote class=se2_quote1 style="_zoom:1;padding:0 8px; margin:0 0 30px 20px; margin-right:15px; border-left:2px solid #cccccc;color:#888888;"><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); white-space-collapse: break-spaces;">개구부에 울타리 등 설치</span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); white-space-collapse: break-spaces;"></span><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); white-space-collapse: break-spaces;">가연성 자재는 별도로 보관</span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(255, 0, 16); font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;">갈탄난로 출입·사용 말아야</span></p></blockquote><p align="center" style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;<img src="http://www.cjchem.co.kr/data/editor/2212/9bccd80539d0132128d011dd837bd3a6_1671083228_33.jpg" title="9bccd80539d0132128d011dd837bd3a6_1671083228_33.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-27116c48-580a-4dd0-b082-8e2b6fa2a407" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-57b0452f-2777-4da3-a5e2-4af8251eba9b" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><u style="text-decoration-skip-ink: none; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">겨울철 건설현장은 낮은 기온으로 인한 신체활동 저하로 추락사 위험이 높을뿐더러 화재 및 폭발 사고 우려가 크다. </u></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-5fdde630-cea5-4c3b-a74c-63ca72957e57" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">또 고용노동부에 따르면 지난 </span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-5159a5f9-83c0-4139-9195-5a961cdc0670" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">10년간 발생한 질식재해의 40%가 건설현장에서 발생</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-db13fb4d-633d-4235-8d5d-bbdc4115b7fe" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">한 것으로 조사됐다. 겨울철 자주 발생하는 사고 유형과 대처 방안에 대해 알아봤다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-f6a58d5b-3a26-4b81-846a-c4bc2267c158" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-ce3ed3c2-1254-468c-8bae-bc49327b2e90" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-110577de-a806-4e3e-bdb4-d22ff6261df1" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-13ab2a22-b9fb-4109-8655-6d595dbc5285" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">◇안전보건공단 ‘동절기 건설현장 안전보건 길잡이’ 중 미끄러짐 자료 캡쳐</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-872117b7-5087-41ad-a1c3-bd0b1f87bfcf" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-9563df2b-8ee0-4256-9a99-7a8473602fd3" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">◇결빙 바닥 추락사 주의=겨울철에는 얼음이 얼면서 미끄러운 바닥에서 넘어져 추락할 위험이 높아진다. 특히 개구부·단부 안전난간 미설치로 인한 추락사고는 겨울철뿐만 아니라 항상 주의를 필요로 하는 재해 유형이다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-90aef25b-c655-42e7-8e85-df8acd54c6dd" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-cc1ee9ac-f7e9-41f8-9854-c5651d3ed581" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-46242f03-21c6-4d36-b176-d54694f26a40" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-f8e95362-2f1f-4f66-9038-b67c92f91228" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">추락사를 방지하기 위해서는 △안전통로 설치 △개구부에 안전난간, 울타리, 덮개 설치 △높이 2미터 이상 추락 위험이 있는 장소 작업 시 안전대 지급 등 조치가 필요하다.</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-974942c4-55e6-4004-bf84-290cb5300d85" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-8eaec7b2-2b15-43e6-b733-2114ec7f362b" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">​</span></p><p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- " id="SE-2bce99f5-ddad-4252-8f74-0aa5af516bf9" style="white-space-collapse: break-spaces; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, &quot;\\\\B098눔고딕&quot;, nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-e36b801a-510e-48c4-a680-201607ee4d7a" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">◇화재 및 폭발 사고=주요 사고 유형으로는 △</span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-9c9fd56c-40be-4fba-b3fc-ac87434350ff" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 16);"><span style="font-weight: 700; background-color: inherit; font-family: inherit;">난방기구 및 전열기구 과열로 인한 화재</span></span><span class="se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   " id="SE-5379e3e6-947a-46be-bb4c-92d9180baac9" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19px; line-height: 